examples: Sir Olof, he rode out at early day, / And so came he unto an Elve -dance gay .

definitions.definition: A rapidly expanding disk-shaped region of red luminosity in the ionosphere , lasting less than a thousandth of a second, which occurs high above energetic cloud-to-ground lightning of positive or negative polarity.

main_definition: ( astronomy , meteorology ) A rapidly expanding disk-shaped region of red luminosity in the ionosphere , lasting less than a thousandth of a second, which occurs high above energetic cloud-to-ground lightning of positive or negative polarity.
